&lt;p&gt;First, we&amp;rsquo;ll take a closer look at creating a triangle based on mash generation, and second - a gradient rhombus!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;chapter-1-mesh-and-triangle&#34;&gt;Chapter 1: Mesh and Triangle!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Within this chapter, let&amp;rsquo;s look at how to make a custom triangle element, as well as tell you in general how this system works.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
